</node>
<node id="World Health Organization">
  <data key="d0">World Health Organization</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The World Health Organization is an international health agency that published the guidelines and provides health leadership globally.&lt;SEP&gt;The World Health Organization (WHO) provides estimates and guidelines for diabetes management and considers it a health priority.&lt;SEP&gt;The World Health Organization is an international public health agency that provides guidance and recommendations on global health issues, including diabetes.&lt;SEP&gt;The World Health Organization is a specialized agency of the United Nations responsible for international public health, involved in various diabetes management and prevention initiatives.&lt;SEP&gt;The World Health Organization is a global health authority responsible for numerous health-related reports and guidelines regarding diabetes.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b253411e54c35aa95f5f9179723bba3b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5384df975133ef2a52113cd3ca0f897e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c4d75b2c01d2448f37de4deec12208fa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-57782c3301473bc8e8dafd9683ab2650&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-942e000d0de99e8628ab9c8bcbe83419</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1770136308</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Egypt">
  <data key="d0">Egypt</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Egypt is the country where the WHO Regional Office for the Eastern Mediterranean is located.&lt;SEP&gt;Egypt is a country that hosts various health consultations and is involved in initiatives by the World Health Organization.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b253411e54c35aa95f5f9179723bba3b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-942e000d0de99e8628ab9c8bcbe83419</data>
