  <data key="d2">The World Health Organization (WHO) is involved in global health efforts, including diabetes prevention and care guidelines.&lt;SEP&gt;The World Health Organization (WHO) is the governing body that defined diabetes mellitus in 1999 and sets guidelines for its management and prevention.&lt;SEP&gt;The World Health Organization recommends that individuals with IFG undergo an OGTT to exclude diabetes diagnosis.</data>
