<node id="Diabetes Mellitus">
  <data key="d0">Diabetes Mellitus</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Diabetes Mellitus is a chronic disease that has seen a rapid increase in prevalence, particularly in the Eastern Mediterranean Region, presenting significant public health challenges. It is characterized by high blood sugar levels (hyperglycemia) resulting from defects in insulin production, insulin action, or both. This condition can be classified mainly into type 1 and type 2 diabetes, addressing how the body processes blood sugar (glucose) and affecting a large portion of the population.

The disorder is multifaceted, impacting carbohydrate, fat, and protein metabolism due to insulin-related defects. It encompasses various types of diabetes, all of which are associated with complications that can affect multiple systems in the body. Common complications related to Diabetes Mellitus include cardiovascular issues, retinopathy, nephropathy, neuropathy, dyslipidaemia, hypoglycaemia, and ketoacidosis, highlighting the importance of effective management and treatment strategies.

Management of Diabetes Mellitus requires careful attention to diet and exercise, along with monitoring blood sugar levels to prevent complications. These chronic conditions necessitate ongoing medical care and public health initiatives to reduce their influence on populations, particularly in areas experiencing higher rates of incidence.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b253411e54c35aa95f5f9179723bba3b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-12fe828372a20b6606e010f0fd5e6263&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-85ef35aaa38ac4f0c032c8bc3f6df559&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a560aca3f99b145384c2b736c2ceea1c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5384df975133ef2a52113cd3ca0f897e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e5fc5e661d0f94cc23c0188b9bbe4e08&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c4d75b2c01d2448f37de4deec12208fa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8361af576f7e73b0bd2ea813976f60b3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d8c827cc2249067692290d6a8a0e8018&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-eb1bc7614fcd68decf9461b3b6290e95&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-21112bd6ed1fe7896dbf55a52bc45a2d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-42a410eaaaed4b7428f5e95a4c7c4580&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-76910bb9e0e5a60b043dd2786bf63e97&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-92fbe09a650e62b7b6ea5d8769440e51&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-25fb88c8ed14936954356d104de095d4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7ef79f22f40772c2060b439008ce485b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a07cef05efd947a538701b4c41b162b1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f15f59b3ff05825a61f252ed8f9a74e1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5e1400e1158e4f7be2283a0366ebf4f2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e8e236a5eba0e1dbf843d32e509da045&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fd4cfbed43aa26af0eef694fecac2177</data>
