<node id="Foot Ulcers">
  <data key="d0">Foot Ulcers</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Foot ulcers are open sores that can occur in diabetic patients and may lead to severe complications, including amputation.&lt;SEP&gt;Foot ulcers are a significant concern in diabetes care, requiring early debridement and potential antibiotic therapy.</data>
