  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Diabetes Education involves imparting knowledge to patients about managing their diabetes through diet, exercise, and medication.&lt;SEP&gt;Diabetes education focuses on increasing knowledge among patients to prevent complications effectively.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-56d9ff3515afac60e7566e41837249a0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a560aca3f99b145384c2b736c2ceea1c</data>
