  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Diabetes Care is a journal that publishes studies and guidelines regarding diabetes management and prevention.&lt;SEP&gt;Diabetes care encompasses various medical practices aimed at managing and treating diabetes effectively.&lt;SEP&gt;Diabetes Care is a publication that includes research and findings related to diabetes, associated with different years.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-56d9ff3515afac60e7566e41837249a0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-57782c3301473bc8e8dafd9683ab2650&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-942e000d0de99e8628ab9c8bcbe83419</data>
