<node id="Tertiary Prevention">
  <data key="d0">Tertiary Prevention</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Tertiary prevention involves measures taken to prevent or manage complications of diabetes that have already developed.&lt;SEP&gt;Tertiary prevention focuses on reducing the impact of established diabetes-related complications, such as blindness and limb amputation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-56d9ff3515afac60e7566e41837249a0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c4d75b2c01d2448f37de4deec12208fa</data>
