  <data key="d0">Primary, Secondary and Tertiary Prevention</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">These terms refer to different levels of diabetes prevention strategies aimed at reducing the incidence and impact of the disease.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-56d9ff3515afac60e7566e41837249a0</data>
