  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The Multidisciplinary Diabetes Team is a group of health professionals collaborating to provide comprehensive care and treatment strategies for diabetes patients.&lt;SEP&gt;The Multidisciplinary Diabetes Team consists of healthcare professionals who collaborate to manage diabetes care for patients.</data>
