<node id="Ophthalmologist">
  <data key="d0">Ophthalmologist</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">The Ophthalmologist is a specialist who conducts annual retinal screenings for diabetes patients to monitor eye health.&lt;SEP&gt;Ophthalmologists are specialists who examine and treat eye conditions, including diabetic retinopathy, and perform necessary screenings and interventions.</data>
