<node id="Insulin Therapy">
  <data key="d0">Insulin Therapy</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Insulin therapy is a treatment method used to control hyperglycemia in individuals with type 1 diabetes and can also be applicable in certain cases of type 2 diabetes.&lt;SEP&gt;Insulin Therapy involves administering insulin to manage blood glucose levels, especially in type 1 diabetes patients.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a560aca3f99b145384c2b736c2ceea1c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-eb1bc7614fcd68decf9461b3b6290e95</data>
