  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Recommended targets are specific levels for metabolic and non-metabolic indicators such as lipid profile, body mass index, and blood pressure for diabetes management.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e5fc5e661d0f94cc23c0188b9bbe4e08</data>
