  <data key="d0">Self-Monitoring of Blood Glucose (SMBG)</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Self-Monitoring of Blood Glucose (SMBG) is a practice recommended for all individuals diagnosed with diabetes as part of self-management education.</data>
