<node id="LDL Cholesterol">
  <data key="d0">LDL Cholesterol</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">LDL Cholesterol is a type of cholesterol that is targeted for reduction in therapy, as high levels are linked to heart disease.&lt;SEP&gt;LDL cholesterol is a type of cholesterol that is often targeted for reduction in therapies due to its association with heart disease.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8361af576f7e73b0bd2ea813976f60b3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-21112bd6ed1fe7896dbf55a52bc45a2d</data>
