<node id="Triglycerides">
  <data key="d0">Triglycerides</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Triglycerides are a type of fat found in the blood, associated with increased cardiovascular risk when elevated.&lt;SEP&gt;Triglycerides are a type of fat found in the blood, with elevated levels posing risks for pancreatitis and cardiovascular disease.&lt;SEP&gt;Triglycerides are a type of fat found in the blood, which can be elevated in certain health conditions and affected by medications.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8361af576f7e73b0bd2ea813976f60b3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-21112bd6ed1fe7896dbf55a52bc45a2d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a07cef05efd947a538701b4c41b162b1</data>
