  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">The Guidelines for the Prevention, Management and Care of Diabetes Mellitus are established recommendations aimed at standardizing diabetes management and providing evidence-based information for health care providers and patients.&lt;SEP&gt;The Guidelines for the Prevention, Management and Care of Diabetes Mellitus provide information on the management of diabetes and related complications.</data>
