  <data key="d2">The United Kingdom Prospective Diabetes Study Group conducted major research influencing diabetes management strategies.&lt;SEP&gt;The United Kingdom Prospective Diabetes Study Group is a research group that has studied the relationship between blood pressure management and diabetes complications.</data>
