  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The Diabetes Control and Complications Trial is a landmark study focusing on the effects of diabetes treatment on complications.&lt;SEP&gt;The Diabetes Control and Complications Trial is a research study that evaluated the effects of tight glycaemic control on complications in patients with diabetes.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-eb1bc7614fcd68decf9461b3b6290e95&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ed87909b4bdb657354ca0eab1450156f</data>
