  <data key="d0">Acute Complications of Diabetes Mellitus</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Acute Complications of Diabetes Mellitus refer to immediate health problems arising in diabetic patients, including hypoglycaemia.&lt;SEP&gt;Acute complications of diabetes mellitus refer to medical issues that arise suddenly and require immediate attention, such as hypoglycaemia and ketoacidosis.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ed87909b4bdb657354ca0eab1450156f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-76910bb9e0e5a60b043dd2786bf63e97</data>
