<node id="Normoglycaemia">
  <data key="d0">Normoglycaemia</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Normoglycaemia is defined as a fasting venous plasma glucose concentration of less than 6.1 mmol/L, observed in individuals with normal glucose tolerance.</data>
