<node id="Ketogenesis">
  <data key="d0">Ketogenesis</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Ketogenesis refers to the process of producing ketone bodies, which can occur in diabetes, especially in type 1 diabetes.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-42a410eaaaed4b7428f5e95a4c7c4580</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1770136333</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Childhood Obesity">
  <data key="d0">Childhood Obesity</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Childhood obesity is identified as a significant factor contributing to the rising prevalence of type 2 diabetes in children and adolescents.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-42a410eaaaed4b7428f5e95a4c7c4580</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1770136333</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Diabetes">
  <data key="d0">Diabetes</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Diabetes is a chronic disease that occurs when the body cannot effectively use insulin, leading to high blood glucose levels.&lt;SEP&gt;Diabetes is a chronic health condition that affects glucose metabolism and requires careful management of diet and lifestyle.&lt;SEP&gt;Diabetes is a metabolic condition that increases the risk of various infections and complications, including atherosclerosis and retinopathy.&lt;SEP&gt;Diabetes is a chronic condition characterized by high blood sugar levels, which can lead to various complications, including neuropathy and foot problems.&lt;SEP&gt;Diabetes is a chronic health condition that requires prioritized health care and prevention strategies to mitigate associated complications.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-2173942c84747feba52cff952903a7f5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8e3bf51a75faa8eb6fe5fe7a0e509efe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e8e236a5eba0e1dbf843d32e509da045&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-eb0252816f7fbee4c50f79ef3ee56063&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-55d2691a8c714949752d249721fec5e7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-12fe828372a20b6606e010f0fd5e6263&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-453e4228f98ddea76e07ce405d13fd32</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1770136333</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Healthy Lifestyle">
  <data key="d0">Healthy Lifestyle</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">A healthy lifestyle involves dietary management, physical activity, and cessation of smoking to reduce the risk of diabetes and its complications.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-2173942c84747feba52cff952903a7f5</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1770136333</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
