<node id="Positive Definite Matrices">
  <data key="d0">Positive Definite Matrices</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Positive definite matrices are those whose eigenvalues are all positive, indicating certain stability and performance characteristics.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f81436ceefbaa6d5dc02610dd8127f9b</data>
