<node id="Complex Numbers">
  <data key="d0">Complex Numbers</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Complex numbers are numbers that include a real part and an imaginary part, often arising in the context of matrix decompositions where certain eigenvalues may be complex.</data>
