  <data key="d0">Neurons</data>
  <data key="d1">naturalobject</data>
  <data key="d2">Neurons are the interconnected cells in the brain responsible for transmitting information and are central to understanding brain functions.&lt;SEP&gt;Neurons are biological cells in the nervous system that transmit information via electrical and chemical signals, foundational to connectionist models.</data>
