  <data key="d0">Neuroscience</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Neuroscience is the scientific study of the nervous system and brain function, influencing theories and models in deep learning and artificial intelligence.&lt;SEP&gt;Neuroscience is the scientific study of the nervous system, providing insights into brain functions and inspiring advancements in machine learning.&lt;SEP&gt;Neuroscience is the scientific study of the nervous system, which benefits from models developed through deep learning techniques.</data>
