<node id="Diagonal Matrices">
  <data key="d0">Diagonal Matrices</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Diagonal matrices consist mostly of zeros, with non-zero entries only on the main diagonal, and are important for efficient computation in linear algebra.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-0403607cb7181d4a13a232d13fec9630</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1770136821</data>
