<node id="Identity Matrix">
  <data key="d0">Identity Matrix</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">The identity matrix is a special type of matrix that does not change any vector when multiplied.&lt;SEP&gt;The Identity Matrix is a special diagonal matrix where all diagonal entries are 1, serving as a multiplicative identity in matrix multiplication.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-0403607cb7181d4a13a232d13fec9630&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9c074e64b3d10aa196769e1082af2cbd</data>
