  <data key="d2">A vector is an ordered array of numbers, often represented in bold typeface, and is used to identify points in space.&lt;SEP&gt;A vector is an element of a vector space, often represented as an array of numbers.&lt;SEP&gt;A vector is an ordered arrangement of numbers, which can represent direction and magnitude in mathematical contexts.</data>
