  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Learning Algorithms are systematic methods employed in machine learning to learn from data and make predictions.&lt;SEP&gt;Learning algorithms are computational methods inspired by biological processes, utilized in the development of artificial neural networks and deep learning.&lt;SEP&gt;Learning Algorithms are systematic methods for processing data to improve performance on a task over time.</data>
