<node id="Linear Algebra">
  <data key="d0">Linear Algebra</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Linear Algebra is a mathematical discipline that deals with vectors, matrices, and linear transformations, crucial for understanding machine learning models.&lt;SEP&gt;Linear algebra is a branch of mathematics crucial for understanding many machine learning algorithms, especially in the context of deep learning.&lt;SEP&gt;Linear algebra is a branch of mathematics that involves the study of vectors, matrices, and scalars, among other mathematical objects.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d9a143ce5c66baaa2cee5e90f9622516&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0d55b6724597822ab76201288059bd8f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2aff4303e41c5babfaf2c4d7bf68299d</data>
