  <data key="d0">Example: Principal Components Analysis</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Principal Components Analysis is a statistical technique used for dimensionality reduction and feature extraction in machine learning, based on Eigenvalue decompositions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d9a143ce5c66baaa2cee5e90f9622516</data>
