  <data key="d0">Hebb</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Donald Hebb is a psychologist noted for his work in neuropsychology, contributing to the principles of learning relevant to neural networks.&lt;SEP&gt;Hebb is a psychologist known for his work related to learning and neural networks, contributing to the field in 1949.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7030ceb5e481db7469c5a663054ab0ff&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5f255acea8c3a7b10af84028b23d7ead</data>
