  <data key="d0">Undercomplete Autoencoders</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Undercomplete Autoencoders are a type of autoencoder where the representation layer has fewer dimensions than the input layer, forcing the network to learn efficient representations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-11ce15464424cd55fa29c0ee197674cc</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1770136870</data>
